summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Eight Avenue Northwest, from East Fifty-fifth Street to East Sixty-fifth Street et al, in the City of Seattle, by grading under Ordinance No. 26260, creating Local Improvement District No. 2449 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
